Sentencas: Scheelite-type, La(x)Ca(1-x)MoO(4+delta) electrolyte powders, are prepared by the sol-gel process.
Titulo: A novel electrolyte for intermediate solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The crystal structure of the samples is determined by employing the technique of X-ray diffraction (XRD).
Titulo: A novel electrolyte for intermediate solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: According to XRD analysis, the continuous series of La(x)Ca(1-x)MoO(4+delta) (0 <= x <= 0.3) solid solutions have the structure of tetragonal scheelite.
Titulo: A novel electrolyte for intermediate solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Their lattice parameters are greater than that of the original sample, and increase with increasing values of x in the La-substituted system.
Titulo: A novel electrolyte for intermediate solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Results of sinterability and electrochemical testing reveal that the performances of La-doped calcium molybdate are superior to that of pure CaMoO(4).
Titulo: A novel electrolyte for intermediate solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The La(0.2)Ca(0.8)MoO(4+delta) sample that achieved 96.5% of the theoretical density was obtained after being sintered at 1250 degrees C for 4h.

Sentencas: The conductivity increases with increasing lanthanum content, and a total conductivity of 7.3 x 10(-3) Scm(-1) at 800 degrees C could be obtained in the La(0.2)Ca(0.8)MoO(4+delta) compound sintered at 1250 degrees C for 4 h. (C) 2009
